ail: Call us toll-free at 1-800-DIABETES (800-342-2383) to donate by credit card. If you prefer you can send a check for your gift by mail. Make a Monthly Donation Become a monthly supporter in the fight against diabetes. For as little as 30¢ a day, you can support lifesaving research and life changing programs that benefit millions of people living with diabetes. It’s a convenient way to spread out your gift over time and can be changed or stopped at any time. Make a Memorial Donation Honor the memory of a family member or friend with a caring gift in their name. Your donation will remember the life and memory of someone you love while enabling us to continue the research that will lead to a cure and provide support to other living with diabetes. Make an Honor Donation Honor a friend or loved one with a gift in their name. It’s a beautiful way to celebrate their life. Honor gifts are meaningful gifts for special occasions like birthdays and anniversaries and includes a FREE e-card or print card acknowledging your gift. Explore: Ways to Give Become a Member General membership to the American Diabetes Association is designed for people with diabetes, their families, friends and caregivers. Wedding Favors In lieu of traditional wedding favors, honor guests or loved ones and order personalized announcements. Workplace Giving As an employee or employer, you can help lead the fight against the deadly consequences of diabetes. Vehicle Donation Donate your old car, truck, boat or RV to help improve the lives of all those affected by diabetes. Planned Giving The Association is grateful to be included in our supporters’ estate plans after they have first provided for their loved ones. Giving Societies Meet some of our most generous donors, whose gifts have made a huge impact in the fight against diabetes. Donate Stocks Donate stocks and mutual fund shares to improve the lives of people with diabetes. Donate Your Collectibles The American Diabetes Association has partnered with Heritage Auctions to provide individuals the opportunity to donate high-value items. Promotions That Give Back Make a contribution each time you participate in these promotional programs. Do-It-Yourself Fundraising & Local Events Create your own fundraising campaign using the Association's online fundraising tools or join a local event. Shopdiabetes.org When you purchase directly from the Association's online store, you are helping to fund diabetes research, education, advocacy and awareness efforts. Team Diabetes By joining Team Diabetes you can participate in an athletic event of your choice — a marathon or triathlon, for example — while helping to raise vital funds to support the mission of the Association. Other Ways to Give There are many different ways to contribute to the Association's mission to stop diabetes. donate en -- Research Saves Lives - 2015-oct-donation-eng.html Research Saves Lives The next miracle in diabetes research begins with you. DONATE TODAY We Can Help (Long) - we-can-help-long.html We Can Help: 1-800-DIABETES (800-342-2383) Monday-Friday, 8:30 a.m. to 8:00 p.m. ET Chat Online Chat Closed Get Local Enter your ZIP to find out what’s going on near you. Enter Zip: Go! O Sponsor -- General Sponsor Thank You promo - sponsor-thank-you.html More from diabetes.org Learn More: Let’s Make Every "Ahhh" Count! - 2016-feb-cigna.html Learn More Let’s Make Every "Ahhh" Count! Get a check-up and share Cigna’s badge to help our mission. Shopdiabetes.org: 150+ diabetes-friendly recipes! - 2016-mar-six-o-clock-scramble-book.html Shopdiabetes.org 150+ diabetes-friendly recipes! Save time with a streamlined system for tasty family dinners! Learn More: 2016 Diabetes Forecast Consumer Guide - l2016-mar-consumer-guide-foot.html Learn More 2016 Diabetes Forecast Consumer Guide Get all you need to know about diabetes tools in one spot. Advocacy: Do Your Part to Stop Diabetes! - 2016-feb-advocacy-petition.html Advocacy Do Your Part to Stop Diabetes! Sign the peti